1. Turn on hotspot
2. sudo su
3. Edit /etc/wpa_supplicant.conf to correct network details (if necessary)
4. Run wpa_supplicant -Dwext -iwlan0 -c/etc/wpa_supplicant.conf -B
    a. if doesn't work, try deleting all other wpa_supplicant sessions running
5. Run echo "nameserver 8.8.8.8" >> /etc/resolv.conf
6. dhclient -R
7. dhclient -v
8. Use 'ping 8.8.8.8' to check for connectivity

